      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 20</em>, <em>Ultimate Combat pg. 134</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 35 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 2 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d4 (small), 1d6 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> 18-20/x2; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> P or S; <strong>Special</strong> deadly</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Light; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Blades, Light</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>These short, slender blades are between 1 to 2 feet long. They are primarily used as back-up weapons, to decapitate defeated enemies, or to commit seppuku (ritual suicide) as a matter of honor. These blades are specifically worn by samurai and are intended to be paired with a katana. Together, this set of blades is referred to as a daisho.</p>"
